Tableau Workbook (Sales_Dashboard.twbx)

Create a New Tableau Workbook:

Open Tableau and connect to the sales_data.csv file.
Load the data into Tableau.
Create Sheets:

Total Sales: Create a sheet that shows total sales using a simple bar chart.
Sales by Region: Create a sheet that visualizes sales by region using a map or a bar chart.
Sales Trend: Create a line chart to show sales trends over time.
Build the Dashboard:

Create a new dashboard.
Drag and drop the sheets you created onto the dashboard.
Add filters and interactive elements to enhance user experience (e.g., date filters, region filters).
Save the Workbook:

Save the workbook as Sales_Dashboard.twbx.
